      <p class="- topic/p ">When the Deal Guidance is based on a Custom Measure and is applicable at the Deal Level
         (Guidance Type), you need to provide custom content for the Deal Guidance pop-up. From the
         cart, you can click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Analyze Deal</uicontrol> button to see the Deal guidance for
